<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.4">
<l>intiraṉu mimaiyavarum muṉivarkaḷum eḻilamainta</l>
<l>cantamalarc catumukaṉuṅ katiravaṉuñ cantiraṉum</l>
<l>entaiyemak karuḷeṉaniṉ ṟaruḷumiṭa meḻilnāṅkai</l>
<l>cuntaranal poḻilpuṭaicūḻ tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place which Indra, the immortals, and the sages,</l>
<l rend="indent">four-faced [Brahmā] of the beauty-endowed, shapely bloom,</l>
<l>The rayed [sun] and the moon always bless as they say,</l>
<l>“Our Father, be gracious to us,’ is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai,</l>
<l>Encircled on [all] sides by fine, lovely groves in beautiful Nāṅkai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
